{"tid":786545,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"委內瑞拉貨幣與加密貨幣石油幣(petro)掛勾　經濟師憂慮惡性通脹加劇","createTime":"2018-08-20T04:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T09:03:26.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"abaf74cb0978eebf3ad7ef162318e28f28aa96f3","tid":786545,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1413389_1_L_20180820110647.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1413389_1_L_20180820110647.jpg&h=fdafe160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉總統馬杜羅宣佈，將當地貨幣與政府加密貨幣石油幣(petro)掛勾，實際令本國貨幣貶值96%。未來數周亦會把最低工資上調30倍，同時提高公司稅稅率並上調高天然氣價格補貼。<br />\n<br />\n馬杜羅周五晚在國營電視台的講話指出，有方法令國家恢復元氣。<br />\n<br />\n不過，經濟師擔心做法會令惡性通脹加劇，指政府缺乏資金，正面對美國制裁同已經出現債務違約。他們憂慮上調公司稅稅率同最低工資會令企業陷入困境，民眾微薄的收入遭受進一步侵蝕。<br />\n<br />\n國際貨幣基金組織較早時預測，今年委內瑞拉通脹率將達到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">百分之一百萬</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ae1294cea7bc9042cf8c0cbcdcaf105c4e5ee6","tid":786545,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T04:10:51.000Z","msg":"委內瑞拉真係好撚on9，遲早搞冧埋鄰國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f8060b1dc5b218a554ff719555ff1ab52cada25","tid":786545,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T04:12:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/4185707/l/fafff9c25c549acacc6fee299e433918.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F4185707%2Fl%2Ffafff9c25c549acacc6fee299e433918.jpg&h=51da6eee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n貨幣嚴重貶值，據週日 (19 日) 的《dolartoday》非官方貨幣數據顯示，去年底 1 美元可兌 8 萬玻利瓦，目前 1 美元卻能兌 592 萬玻利瓦 (Bolivar，委內瑞拉幣)。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4830bd237ee41cb7f8599451d0af7bb8f95d072","tid":786545,"uid":10340,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T04:15:40.000Z","msg":"有冇計過陰司紙面值高啲定委內瑞拉貨幣高啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98ee5dfb2d7ff702dfd2853f20b1882f2b85627","tid":786545,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T04:15:46.000Z","msg":"委內瑞拉是全世界謀殺率最高的國家，卡拉卡斯是全世界謀殺率最高的城市。大部分的謀殺與其他暴力犯罪都不會破案。卡拉卡斯周圍山丘上的貧窮社區非常危險。2012年，卡拉卡斯被認為是全世界第三危險的城市，謀殺率為每 100,000 人 119 次。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係乜撚野鬼國黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b83d17190fa088f5f0b7d521d9b9c12218da892","tid":786545,"uid":22913,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T04:17:38.000Z","msg":"同美國鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e183b677771a88b7c2248e6ac3c04573ad2c750","tid":786545,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T04:40:58.000Z","msg":"變廢紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fba44d5d69418575bce8b35cf8f6313b19aa7ba","tid":786545,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T04:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a664c2dc7dbed80f0c5e005f0ac6fb67f3b76479","tid":786545,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T04:48:09.000Z","msg":"幾時引入委国外傭及妓女<br />\n我相信咁先可以將外匯帶返本國"},{"pid":"ef191514a33e1a4edff1f08bc78d342f28975cfd","tid":786545,"uid":686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":